1
00:00:01,380 --> 00:00:03,830
I don't get it.

2
00:00:04,710 --> 00:00:05,750
President Kurogane put you and me...

3
00:00:05,790 --> 00:00:07,080
...together...

4
00:00:07,460 --> 00:00:08,880
...because he was betting on the AI sector's...

5
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:10,330
...future growth.

6
00:00:10,710 --> 00:00:12,670
After you married Sami,

7
00:00:12,670 --> 00:00:14,460
your business took off.
All because...

8
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:16,250
...you're his daughter's husband.

9
00:00:16,540 --> 00:00:19,130
President Kurogane gave you contracts...

10
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:25,210
...not because of your talent.

11
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:27,460
You have no talent.

12
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,000
It was all...

13
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:30,500
...Sami's doing.

14
00:00:33,080 --> 00:00:34,080
And another thing.

15
00:00:37,210 --> 00:00:38,580
I've known for a while...

16
00:00:38,830 --> 00:00:39,960
...who you really are.

17
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:42,290
Box Cutter Boy.

18
00:00:43,630 --> 00:00:44,630
But...

19
00:00:44,830 --> 00:00:45,830
What?

20
00:00:46,330 --> 00:00:48,750
I happen to know
something even wilder.

21
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:50,460
What is it?

22
00:00:50,670 --> 00:00:51,670
Her...

23
00:00:52,710 --> 00:00:53,710
...true identity.

24
00:00:55,290 --> 00:00:56,380
Her husband...

25
00:00:57,380 --> 00:00:59,290
...is the one who assaulted you
in high school.

26
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,830
Shut up.

27
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:05,710
Shut up, shut up, shut up, shut up!

28
00:01:08,210 --> 00:01:09,380
These two...

29
00:01:10,380 --> 00:01:11,830
...are lesbians.

30
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:12,670
A couple.

31
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:13,920
The heiress to a major...

32
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,290
...Japanese corporation.

33
00:01:15,630 --> 00:01:16,630
So what?

34
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,130
Is there a problem with that?

35
00:01:20,130 --> 00:01:21,130
President Kurogane.

36
00:01:21,460 --> 00:01:22,460
This woman...

37
00:01:22,670 --> 00:01:24,500
She has repeatedly...

38
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,580
...harassed your daughter.

39
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,540
You must punish her.

40
00:01:29,290 --> 00:01:30,290
That won't be necessary.

41
00:01:31,290 --> 00:01:32,130
That matter...

42
00:01:32,130 --> 00:01:33,580
...has already been resolved.

43
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:35,290
Damn it!

44
00:01:35,290 --> 00:01:35,830
Damn it.

45
00:01:36,290 --> 00:01:38,040
Your illegal transactions...

46
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:39,880
...and all your criminal activities...

47
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:41,830
...are enough to press charges.

48
00:01:42,420 --> 00:01:44,790
You can think about what you've done in prison.

49
00:01:45,460 --> 00:01:46,710
You've lost.

50
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:48,420
Nakama Kaito.
